ckoutservice->shippingservice\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"显著延迟传播至最下游的 CartService（hipstershop.CartService/EmptyCart 和 hipstershop.CartService/GetCart 的延迟倍数超过190倍）。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"checkoutservice 调用 cartservice 的多个接口延迟明显增加，尤其在 EmptyCart 接口（从近15802毫秒增加至 7567387毫秒）。\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"shippingservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"在链路中的 ShippingService 延迟倍数为3倍，与 GetQuote 的调用服务异常直接相关。\",\n      \"evidence\": \"checkoutservice 调用 ShippingService 的 GetQuote 接口耗时从 199 毫秒延至 691 毫秒。\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n``` \n\n依据分析，异常根源在调用链下游的 `cartservice` 和 `shippingservice`。", "current_hypothesis": "aiops-k8s-07 is the root cause due to node_memory_MemAvailable_bytes exhaustion, causing resource contention for CartService pods and subsequent latency spikes."}
